{"tid":293131,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來, 古代中文, 動詞要加s","createTime":"2017-06-22T02:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T07:51:13.000Z","uid":121784,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a37bff6535ac978511b5dad0cc0f4d67f347e90","tid":293131,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:23:00.000Z","msg":"原來, 秦朝以前, 中文某些字, 變成動詞, 讀音要加s<br />\n<br />\n例:<br />\n數(廣東話第三聲, &quot;數&quot;字), 古音srok<br />\n數(廣東話第二聲, &quot;數&quot;人頭), 古音sroks<br />\n<br />\n例:<br />\n惡(惡人), 古音ak<br />\n惡(憎惡), 古音aks"},{"pid":"6c6fa90ca2aa7ece59ccc129ad542ae44fb2a380","tid":293131,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9461a22e078a9ba45e8f4a3576b7ffe246e9e43a","tid":293131,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"d9e56c38297dc244759caa8454784058cddccc25","tid":293131,"uid":107938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Source?</blockquote><br />\n鄭張尚芳嘅上古音系"},{"pid":"c661e4d81665ea347f67cb25a321b85ab6e9e3b0","tid":293131,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Source?</blockquote><br />\n事實<br />\n<br />\n之前讀古音學過<br />\n<br />\nYoutube有人將tvb既古裝劇譯做古音<br />\n<br />\n好似單音節既英文咁，尾音加s"},{"pid":"146da2ac7763a334b2d0e01318ffa9e268bdbe12","tid":293131,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"上古漢語接近原始印歐語"},{"pid":"7421863a31e59d7e9043ac532cfbb36d6107dfb2","tid":293131,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上古漢語接近原始印歐語</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n差好遠，印歐語詞尾變化多好多<br />\n基本字詞亦完全不同"},{"pid":"c5436e665bb2f5f3257f9eb0ea0afd473d529085","tid":293131,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上古漢語接近原始印歐語</blockquote><br />\n我從聖經中找到證據，人類的語言本身都是類近於希伯來文，只是人類要挑戰上帝，興建巴別塔，上帝便將人類的語言分成許多種，使人類不能團結。"},{"pid":"e9449aa12a9f30994348dbd3510b8aeed7c877c3","tid":293131,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"個D咩上古音系根本得淡笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就好似太極咁 多人吹捧"},{"pid":"80d6f73969677db66c21d8f1560516bb49e7aae3","tid":293131,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"我知道 角落 古音係 glok"},{"pid":"e2d0c2832b3b1156d8e22946c95a53edd198659f","tid":293131,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"其實點研究返出黎?"},{"pid":"bc594b6d7d991a3132bd07ce731e61b1e112e2ef","tid":293131,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實點研究返出黎?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先研復原唐代音，因為古代韻書，字典有詳細講，亦可由日文漢字當時的拼音作旁証。<br />\n<br />\n然後，再由唐音推算出先秦古音。"},{"pid":"8dc333ffc1a7a7568b1822c295a7430bbd82f4bf","tid":293131,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知道 角落 古音係 glok</blockquote><br />\n睇wiki, 角係klok<br />\n<br />\n以前中文有分清k濁g和送氣kh，而家廣東話同普通話得返k同kh<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地學拉丁語系如法文西班牙文葡萄牙文好蝕底，<br />\n我d葡萄牙朋友，好易分出g,k<br />\n但我聽唔出，而且想發g音好易變成k音，產生不少誤會。。"},{"pid":"937247f04aaf7173eda066a8a10effc072bb9a79","tid":293131,"uid":4955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea28f1b9c5ad32e3f9a01bf5785c8f6d0ca6958","tid":293131,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"上古漢語好似好多抖脷音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0716ecad6852a3405bb65e89c27b4e38338409d9","tid":293131,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"廣東話變聲調算唔算屈折既一種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如你舉既數第二聲係動詞, 第三聲係名詞"}]}